title: "AI Agent Action-Safety Audit: harness and battery"
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Jiahao
    family-names: Zhang
repository-code: "https://github.com/hugoii/llm-agent-audit"
url: "https://github.com/hugoii/llm-agent-audit"
abstract: >-
  An open, dependency-free harness that grades a tool-using LLM agent's
  tool-call trace against a fixed, OWASP-mapped battery of adversarial
  scenarios, used to measure action-safety across model configurations.
keywords:
  - LLM agents
  - tool use
  - prompt injection
  - authorization
  - AI security
